# research
 
 - nano compost: what is the smallest unit of compost?
 - worm farming: what is the smallest unit of worm reproduction, in cubes
 - sticks on mud prints in the field
 - better solar rig for public spaces
 - aluminum battery in a cube
 - rock grinding machines
 - electron beam lithography for self-replicating geometric data storage 
 - use the micro linear positioning on the DVD drive to do micro storage of data, use the optics to read back the data, to make self-replicating data
 - build an analog media storage format using trash based on DVD drives
